review_blob: A very slight bitterness to it....it is a 50 IBU. Not overly strong, I do like a strong bitter but this allows for a bitter taste if you want to have multiple beverages in an evening.
This has a taste I just cant place. Its a good taste just need more to figure it out.
beer_name: Rogue Captain Sigs Deadliest Ale (Northwestern Ale)

review_blob: Black in colour with a caramel colour head. I am surprised I like this as its a Belgian and I generally am not a fan of Belgian beers. I also love the Phillips bottles.
Love this beer, from the label to the aroma to the flavours. It unfortunate its not as readily available in my area.
